text: int main ( ) { int t ; scanf ( "%d" , & t ) ; while ( t -- ) { long int a , b , c ; scanf ( "%d %d" , & a , & b ) ; c = a * b ; if ( a < b ) { int temp = a ; a = b ; b = temp ; } while ( b != 0 ) { int rem = a % b ; a = b ; b = rem ; } printf ( "%d %d\n" , a , c / a ) ; } return 0 ; }
